  "text": "Columns (4) and (5) show that the share of workers in small firms decreased disproportionately more among high FD sectors when access to credit fell. This could be because small firms are more dependent on external finance than their larger peers [CITATION_1] Beck and Demirguc-Kunt, 2016; [CITATION_2] ).",
